==印度-伊朗语族借词==
尼瓦尔语是伊朗化最厉害的汉藏语。下面是一些借自[[印度-伊朗语族|印度-伊朗语族]]的基础词：<ref>From the review article on "Dictionary of classical Newari compiled from manuscript sources." With the financial support of Toyota Foundation, Japan, Nepal Bhasa Dictionary Committee. Cwasā Pāsā. Kathmandu: Modern Printing Press, Jamal 2000.{{ISBN|99933-31-60-0}}"</ref>{{rp|XXXV, 530}}

